                <Class>
                    <__p_name>BlockBase</__p_name>
                    <__p_description>This is the block base class. It partially implements the abstract block class. This base class implements all required operators defined in the abstract class. It implements all interfaces required for the parent child relationship, loading to and from XML, and basic properties. Default interfaces for volatility above and below are implemented that both return false.</__p_description>
