                <Class>
                    <__p_name>ParserBase</__p_name>
                    <__p_description>This is the parser base class. It partially implements the abstract parser class. This base class implements all interfaces for accessing the current file being read, the call operator for executing parsing itself, reader lookup, and setting the root path.

