                    </Function>
                </Class>
                <Class>
                    <__p_name>ReaderBase</__p_name>
                    <__p_description>This is the reader base class. It partially implements the abstract reader class. This base class handles the saving of its parent parser or reader, all file access interfaces that call their parent parser's methods of the same name, setting its key, getting its key, and the main call operator interface for parsing. It provides methods for accessing the currently open file of its parent parser with methods of the same name.

An interface for parsing this parent parser's currently open file is provided for convenience. This interface is a sub task of the main call operator implemented by this base class, and must set this reader's key before returning.</__p_description>
                    <__p_parents>AbstractReader</__p_parents>
