                        <Class>
                            <__p_name>BlockViewDock</__p_name>
                            <__p_description>This is the block view dock class. It interfaces itself to a project view, providing a detailed view of the currently indexed block. It connects the appropriate signal to listen for the current index of the view to change. The detailed view is presented in a Qt label as rich text.</__p_description>
