                        <Class>
                            <__p_name>PlainTextEdit</__p_name>
                            <__p_description>This is the plain text class. It provides additional functionality to its inherited class. Spell checking highlights misspelled words. A popup shortcut is provided to open a larger text editor dialog that has additional spell checking functionality. Spell checking and the editor dialog popup shortcut features can be enabled or disabled.</__p_description>
